textTemplates.name: welcome_question_lref_tt
textTemplates.text:
We are currently assessing the water quality of our citizens. We'd love to hear from you about what types of conditions you are experiencing. The survey should only take 5 minutes, and your responses are completely anonymous.


If you have any questions about the survey, please email us: support-gadugiportal@cherokee.org


We really appreciate your input!
